    6254 [label=<Google Policy Classification: <B><FONT COLOR="/svg/forestgreen">notice</FONT></B><BR />notice - These licenses contain few restrictions, allowing original or modified<BR />third-party software to be shipped in any product without endangering or<BR />encumbering our source code. All of the licenses in this category do, however,<BR />have an "original Copyright notice" or "advertising clause", wherein any<BR />external distributions must include the notice or clause specified in the<BR />license.>
         ,fillcolor="beige;1"
         ,shape=plaintext];
